LiveDemo :https://a-team-machine-task.vercel.app/

This is the frontend of the ATeam Machine Task project, developed by Muhammed Aadil NV.
It showcases a modern recipe dashboard built using React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and Framer Motion, focusing on smooth UI animations, responsiveness, and clean architecture.

